videos.headline: Henigan's 31-yard TD puts Memphis on the board
videos.description: Seth Henigan finds Asa Martin who takes it 31 yards to the house to put the Tigers on the board first.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Seth Henigan with 31-yard touchdown Pass to Asa Martin vs. East Carolina) 2021/11/13 ESHEET

videos.headline: Holton Ahlers muscles his way into the end zone
videos.description: ECU QB Holton Ahlers keeps it himself and muscles his way into the end zone to tie the game at 7-7.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Holton Ahlers rushes in for 2-yard Rushing TD) 2021/11/13 ESHEET

videos.headline: Seth Henigan connects with Eddie Lewis for 75-yard Memphis TD
